  "name": "DatabaseMons",
  "symbol": "script_15",
  "description": "Extremely inefficient but OK if you want to ensure battle monster data and enemy match. Use wLookingFor beforehand to tell it to look for enemy or ally data. temp3 is a var for temporarily setting the species to lookup and could probably be replaced by something else.",
